d Redis caching for frequently accessed data, which visibly reduced database load and kept response times low during testing.\n• Packaged the application with Docker to ensure consistent environments across development and staging.\n• Used Cloudinary API to handle image resizing and lazy loading, improving frontend performance on slower networks."}', '{"education": {"score": 2.0, "reason": "Ứng viên đã tốt nghiệp cử nhân Information Technology vào năm 2026, phù hợp với yêu cầu của vị trí."}, "self_evaluation": {"score": 1.0, "reason": "Đánh giá tự đánh giá của ứng viên chỉ đề cập đến một số kỹ năng cơ bản và chưa rõ ràng liên kết chúng với sự phát triển nghề nghiệp cụ thể."}, "work_experience": {"score": 3.5, "reason": "Ứng viên có ít nhất một năm kinh nghiệm làm việc trong môi trường công nghệ thông tin, bao gồm các dự án liên quan đến backend và frontend phát triển."}, "basic_information": {"score": 1.5, "reason": "Ứng viên đã cung cấp đầy đủ thông tin cá nhân và không có bất kỳ thiếu sót nào."}, "skills_specialties": {"score": 4.0, "reason": "Ứng viên đã chứng minh khả năng sử dụng Java, Spring Boot, Spring MVC, Spring Data JPA, Spring Security, JWT, WebSocket, JUnit 5, Mockito trong các dự án thực tế. Các kỹ năng này phù hợp với yêu cầu của vị trí."}}', 'Tổng điểm đánh giá là 12.0, ứng viên có thể cần cải thiện khả năng liên kết giữa các kỹ năng và sự phát triển nghề nghiệp cụ thể để đạt được mức tối đa.', 12, false, 'new', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO public.cv_infos (id, cv_file_id, full_name, email, phone, date_of_birth, address, summary, educations, created_at, updated_at, "position", total_experience_years, raw_text, profile_data, quality_details, quality_reason, quality_score, is_marked, tag, note, work_type) VALUES (116, 164, 'Dinh Quan Nguyen', 'dinhquan.data@example.com', '+84 945 678 123', '2003-08-20', 'Hanoi, Vietnam', 'Highly motivated IT graduate seeking a Data Engineer Intern position to apply and develop skills in building scalable data pipelines, data collection tooling, and analytical systems. Eager to contribute to data-driven projects in a large enterprise environment and grow into a senior data engineering role, with a long-term focus on real-time data processing and enterprise-scale data architecture.', '[{"field": "Information Technology", "degree": "Bachelor of Information Technology", "university": "University of Information Technology", "graduation_year": "2025"}]', '2026-06-24 23:11:36.797097', '2026-06-24 16:11:44.070261', 'Data Engineer Intern', 0, 'Dinh Quan Nguyen
Data Engineer Intern
DOB: 20/08/2003 | Hanoi, Vietnam
dinhquan.data@example.com | +84 945 678 123 linkedin.com/in/dinhquandata | github.com/dinhquandata
CAREER GOALS
Highly motivated IT graduate seeking a Data Engineer Intern position to apply and develop skills in building scalable data pipelines, data collection tooling, and analytical systems. Eager to contribute to data-driven projects in a large enterprise environment and grow into a senior data engineering role, with a long-term focus on real-time data processing and enterprise-scale data architecture.
EDUCATION
University of Information Technology
2021 – 2025
Bachelor of Information Technology GPA: 3.35/4.0
• Relevant coursework: Database Design & Development, Business Intelligence, Enterprise Web Software Development, Requirements Management, Website Design & Development.
PROJECTS
Retail Data Platform | Python, dbt Core, Apache Airflow, PostgreSQL, MinIO, Docker, Prophet 05/2026
Role: Full Stack Data Engineer
• Architected an end-to-end data platform for Vietnamese retail stores (electronics, home goods), ingesting data from KiotViet API (OAuth2, 15-min incremental polling) and Excel files into PostgreSQL via idempotent upsert with row_hash change detection.
• Built a 4-layer dbt transformation pipeline (raw → staging → intermediate → mart) with 11 models, 97 total tests (86 schema + 11 custom), achieving 97% test pass rate and enforcing referential integrity across all marts.
• Designed 6 analytical marts covering daily sales trends, RFM segmentation (12 customer segments), Customer 360 with churn probability, product performance ranking, inventory health (5 alert levels), and 90-day demand forecasting using Facebook Prophet with Vietnamese holiday calendars.
• Orchestrated 3 Airflow DAGs (daily ETL at 02:00, near-real-time KiotViet polling every 15 min, weekly Prophet forecast on Sundays) with retry/backoff, execution timeouts, and Zalo/email failure notifications.
• Containerised all 8 services (Airflow, dbt, PostgreSQL, MinIO, Metabase, pgAdmin) via Docker Compose, enabling one-command local deployment and straightforward cloud migration.
Lumiere AI Analytics tools | FastAPI, React, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, OpenAI API, Docker 08/2025 – 12/2025
Role:
Full Stack Developer
• Designed and implemented a full-stack data analytics platform enabling SMEs to query their data in natural language, auto-generate SQL, and receive AI-driven visualisations and insights.
End-to-End ELT Pipeline | Python, Apache Airflow, AWS S3/EC2/RDS, PostgreSQL, Docker, SQL 01/2026
Role: Full Stack Data Engineer
• Built a production-style ELT pipeline ingesting data from CSV and REST API sources into AWS S3 as a raw staging zone, then loading into PostgreSQL RDS for downstream analytics.
• Designed a Kimball-style star schema with 3 dimension tables ( dim.customer , dim.product , dim.date ) and 2 fact tables ( fact.orders , fact.daily_sales ), supporting time-series and segment-based reporting queries.
• Orchestrated the full workflow with an Apache Airflow DAG featuring incremental watermark processing, idempotent tasks, automatic retry policies, and XCom-based metadata passing between stages.
• Documented system architecture, data lineage, and built-in data quality checks (schema validation, referential integrity, duplicate prevention).
WORK EXPERIENCE
NTT DATA VDS Co., Ltd
02/2026 – 05/2026
AI Intern
• Designed and implemented an AI prototype that auto-generates and validates test cases from User Stories and SRS, targeting a 50% reduction in manual QA effort.
• Built a hybrid LLM architecture (local on-premise + OpenAI API), conducting trade-off analysis on accuracy, latency, and cost to balance data security and reasoning capability.
• Engineered prompt templates for functional, negative, and edge-case scenarios; enforced JSON/Gherkin output format for direct integration into automation pipelines.
• Implemented requirement-to-test traceability for automated coverage checks and early detection of missing or inconsistent scenarios.
• Delivered SRS, architecture design docs, and performance evaluation reports to international documentation standards.
Soi Bien Trung Thuc Joint Stock Company
01/2021 – 06/2021
Content Marketing
• Managed 3 social media pages and 2 groups (>3,000 members); ran multi-channel ad campaigns generating over 40M VND/day in revenue.
• Produced weekly/monthly ad spend reports and handled logistics, order closing, and inventory sourcing.
TECHNICAL SKILLS
• Data Engineering: Apache Airflow, dbt Core, ETL/ELT pipeline design, Star schema / Kimball modeling, Incremental loading, Data quality testing
• Databases: PostgreSQL, MySQL (SQL DDL/DML, Joins, Aggregation, Window functions); basic NoSQL awareness
• Programming: Python (pandas, NumPy, SQLAlchemy, requests, pytest), SQL
• Data Visualisation: Tableau, Metabase
CERTIFICATIONS & AWARDS
• Google Data Analytics Professional Certificate | Google 2024 • English Aptis B2 (168/200, equivalent IELTS 6.0) | British Council 2024 • "Promising Award" – Startup Competition in Agricultural Sector (AGRIUP 2025) 2025', '{"data": {"job_position": "Data Engineer Intern", "self_evaluation": "Highly motivated IT graduate seeking a Data Engineer Intern position to apply and develop skills in building scalable data pipelines, data collection tooling, and analytical systems. Eager to contribute to data-driven projects in a large enterprise environment and grow into a senior data engineering role, with a long-term focus on real-time data processing and enterprise-scale data architecture.", "work_experience": [{"company": "NTT DATA VDS Co., Ltd", "duration": "02/2026 - 05/2026", "position": "AI Intern", "responsibility": "Designed and implemented an AI prototype that auto-generates and validates test cases from User Stories and SRS, targeting a 50% reduction in manual QA effort. Built a hybrid LLM architecture (local on-premise + OpenAI API), conducted trade-off analysis on accuracy, latency, and cost to balance data security and reasoning capability. Engineered prompt templates for functional, negative, and edge-case scenarios; enforced JSON/Gherkin output format for direct integration into automation pipelines. Implemented requirement-to-test traceability for automated coverage checks."}], "basic_information": {"name": "Dinh Quan Nguyen", "email": "dinhquan.data@example.com", "phone": "+84 945 678 123", "status": "Completed", "address": "Hanoi, Vietnam", "date_of_birth": "2003-08-20"}, "education_background": [{"field": "Information Technology", "degree": "Bachelor of Information Technology", "university": "University of Information Technology", "graduation_year": "2025"}], "skills_and_specialties": {"skills": ["Python", "dbt Core", "Apache Airflow", "PostgreSQL", "MinIO", "Docker", "Prophet", "FastAPI", "React", "TypeScript", "AWS S3/EC2/RDS"], "certifications": []}, 