hoanganh.da@example.com | +84 933 444 555
linkedin.com/in/hoanganh-da | github.com/hoanganh-da
SUMMARY
Data-driven Industrial Management student (Business Administration) at HCMUT. Passionate about analytics and actively enhancing technical skills in IT and database management to transform complex data into actionable business insights as a Data Analyst.
TECHNICAL SKILLS
• Data Analysis & Modeling: Data Warehouse (DW) Design, Decision Support Systems (DSS), Data Mining, Machine Learning (Regression, Classification).
• AI-Assisted Analytics (Vibe Coding): Expert in leveraging GitHub Copilot, Cursor AI, and Gemini to accelerate SQL querying, Python scripting (Pandas, Scikit-learn), and data cleaning.
• Generative AI & LLMs: Proficient in deploying and prompting local LLMs (Llama 3 via Ollama) for automated insight generation and text data analysis.
• Tools & Platforms: Web AI Apps integration, Power BI/Tableau for DSS visualization, SQL Server/PostgreSQL.
KEY PROJECTS
Formula 1 Race Strategy DW/DSS System
Role: Team Leader (Managed a team of 5)
Tech Stack: Cursor, GitHub Copilot (Vibe Coding Workflow), SQL Server, Python, Ollama (Llama 3), Power BI.
• Data Architecture: Designed and implemented a Star Schema for the Data Warehouse, optimizing Fact tables (race results, pit stops) and Dimension tables (tire specs, drivers) for high-performance querying.
• AI-Powered ETL & Refactoring: Utilized GitHub Copilot & Cursor to engineer and refactor complex Python/SQL scripts for cleaning and normalizing historical F1 datasets across multiple seasons.
• Advanced Analytics & Mining: Integrated local LLMs via Ollama (Llama 3) and applied Data Mining techniques to analyze tire degradation patterns and predict race rankings based on real-time variables.
• Insight Visualization: Built comprehensive Power BI dashboards to visualize the correlation between tire strategies and final podium positions, providing deep insights into team performance.
WORK EXPERIENCE
MB BANK | Individual Customer Dept Intern
Jun 2024 – Oct 2025
• Analyzed customer financial needs to recommend optimal banking products (Loans, Digital accounts, QR solutions).
• Managed documentation and procedures for mortgage and consumer loans, ensuring accuracy and regulatory compliance.
• Facilitated international remittance processes, enhancing customer service efficiency and transaction security.
POPEYES & BANH MI OI | Service Crew (Lobby & Cashier) Jun 2023 – Jun 2024
• Managed inventory levels and stock rotation for food and supplies to ensure operational continuity.
• Performed order verification (cross-checking app and in-store orders) to maintain 100% data and delivery accuracy.
• Developed problem-solving and communication skills by handling customer requests in a high-paced retail environment.
VOLUNTEER ACTIVITIES
• Summer Volunteer Campaign (Mua He Xanh): Organized community support activities and managed logistics for a team of 15+ volunteers in rural areas.
EDUCATION
HCM City University of Technology (HCMUT)
Bachelor of Industrial Management, Major in Business Administration | GPA: 2.6/4.0
2021 – 2026
CERTIFICATIONS & LANGUAGES
• Microsoft Office Specialist (MOS): Excel, PowerPoint, Word.
• TOEIC: 645/990.
• English: Professional Working Proficiency.', '{"data": {"job_position": "Data Analyst Intern", "self_evaluation": "Data-driven Industrial Management student (Business Administration) at HCMUT. Passionate about analytics and actively enhancing technical skills in IT and database management to transform complex data into actionable business insights as a Data Analyst.", "work_experience": [{"company": "MB BANK", "duration": "Jun 2024 – Oct 2025", "position": "Individual Customer Dept Intern", "responsibility": "Analyzed customer financial needs to recommend optimal banking products, managed documentation and procedures for mortgage and consumer loans, facilitated international remittance processes."}, {"company": "POPEYES & BANH MI OI", "duration": "Jun 2023 – Jun 2024", "position": "Service Crew (Lobby & Cashier)", "responsibility": "Managed inventory levels and stock rotation, performed order verification to maintain accuracy, developed problem-solving and communication skills in a high-paced retail environment."}], "basic_information": {"name": "Hoang Anh Nguyen", "email": "hoanganh.da@example.com", "phone": "+84 933 444 555", "status": "Completed", "address": "Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam", "date_of_birth": "2002-12-08"}, "education_background": [{"field": "Major in Business Administration", "degree": "Bachelor of Industrial Management", "university": "HCM City University of Technology (HCMUT)", "graduation_year": "2026"}], "skills_and_specialties": {"skills": ["Data Analysis & Modeling", "AI-Assisted Analytics", "Generative AI & LLMs", "Tools & Platforms"], "certifications": ["Microsoft Office Specialist (MOS): Excel, PowerPoint, Word", "TOEIC: 645/990", "AWS Certified DevOps", "IELTS 7.5"]}, "total_experience_years": 0}, "cv_id": "29a04656-0a3a-48cc-9e2a-9e7828996883", "status": "success", "message": "CV đã được trích xuất cấu trúc thành công và lưu kho dưới dạng Semantic Chunking.", "raw_text": "Hoang Anh Nguyen\nData Analyst Intern\nDOB: 12/08/2002 | Ho Chi Min