PERSONAL PROFILE
Results-driven AI Engineer with a strong foundation in Software Engineering, specializing in Computer Vision, NLP, and Multi-modal RAG systems. Proven ability to own the entire ML lifecycle—from researching Vision-Language Models (VLMs) for complex video data to developing robust backend APIs for secure, internal deployments. Adept at translating technical trade-offs into strategic business insights for leadership, delivering scalable and enterprise-ready AI solutions.
