d Redis caching for frequently accessed data, which visibly reduced database load and kept response times low during testing.\n• Packaged the application with Docker to ensure consistent environments across development and staging.\n• Used Cloudinary API to handle image resizing and lazy loading, improving frontend performance on slower networks."}', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, 'new', NULL, NULL);
