• AI Assistants: Gemini, Claude (for code debugging, query optimization, and rapid learning)
• Visualization & Business Tools: Power BI, Microsoft Excel (Pivot Tables, VLOOKUP, Data Processing), PowerPoint, LaTeX, Git
