• Technologies: ASP.NET Core, SQL Server, Ocelot API Gateway, REST API.', '{"data": {"job_position": "Intern Backend Developer", "self_evaluation": "Backend-focused Full Stack Developer with strong experience in building scalable RESTful APIs using TypeScript (Express.js) and ASP.NET Core. Experienced in designing real-time systems, authentication mechanisms, and database optimization. Passionate about clean architecture, performance optimization, and writing maintainable code.", "work_experience": [{"company": "", "duration": "07/2025 – 02/2026", "position": "Full Stack Developer", "responsibility": "Developed a real-time notification system with online/offline status tracking using Socket.IO. Implemented robust authentication & authorization using JWT, Session, and Cookie (similar to Google auth flow). Built core features including post management (like, comment, share) and group management (member approval, sorting posts). Designed a user management module (profile editing, friend suggestions, relationship management) and a feed algorithm based on user preferences. Optimized performance through cursor/offset pagination, server-side folder image storage to reduce database load, and data caching."}, {"company": "", "duration": "12/2025 – 01/2026", "position": "Backend Developer", "responsibility": "Built endpoints for real-time monitoring and near real-time analytics. Dynamic revenue reporting, and detailed customer/order statistics aggregations."}], "basic_information": {"name": "Le Hai Dang", "email": "lehaidang.dev@example.com", "phone": "+84 912 345 678", "status": "Completed", "address": "Hanoi, Vietnam", "date_of_birth": "2005-09-24"}, "education_background": [{"field": "", "degree": "Software Engineering", "university": "Hanoi University of Industry", "graduation_year": ""}], "skills_and_specialties": {"skills": ["TypeScript/JavaScript", "C#", "HTML/CSS", "Jest"], "certifications": []}, "total_experience_years": 0}, "cv_id": "ad89564f-e78d-4947-a015-c44907fc