PERSONAL SUMMARY
Backend-focused Full Stack Developer with strong experience in building scalable RESTful APIs using TypeScript (Express.js) and ASP.NET Core. Experienced in designing real-time systems, authentication mechanisms, and database optimization. Passionate about clean architecture, performance optimization, and writing maintainable code.
